{"tid":1003374,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"把歌讓給IZ*ONE被嘆「錯失大紅機會」　CLC認：音都錄好了⋯","createTime":"2019-01-31T15:02:03.000Z","updateTime":"2019-02-01T11:06:25.000Z","uid":74065,"like":27,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":18,"replies":[{"pid":"bd26bd918793233f41f02a788883eec4eb131027","tid":1003374,"uid":74065,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-31T15:02:03.000Z","msg":"日韓限定女團IZ*ONE出身自節目《Produce 48》，雖然一開始聲勢比不上前兩季，但她們出道曲《La Vie en Rose》沒有選擇可預期的清純少女風，讓歌迷耳目一新，反而因此而爆紅。但後來該歌曲被發現本來是要給7人女團CLC演唱，CLC近期也委婉的證實了此事。<br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn2.ettoday.net/images/3877/d3877782.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn2.ettoday.net%2Fimages%2F3877%2Fd3877782.jpg&h=5f1418d2&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n▲南韓女團CLC睽違一年多回歸。（圖／CFP）<br />\n<br />\nCLC相隔一年，30日帶著新輯《No.1》回歸。<span style=\"color: red;\">記者會上被問到錯失《La Vie en Rose》一事，被網友稱讚「聲音超適合那首歌」的主唱睿恩坦言：「因為已經錄完音，之後聽到（歌給了IZ*ONE）的消息雖然很驚訝，但其實也是音樂圈常有的事。雖然感到可惜，但不會難過。」也稱讚道：「我覺得這首歌找到更好的主人。」</span><br />\n<br />\n《La Vie en Rose》由舞團「Freemind」編舞，她們在IZ*ONE出道後上傳練舞室影片，有著一開始招牌的花瓣編舞，也有彩元靠著咲良跟仁美手搭的橋前進的畫面，當然brigde部分，由恩菲站在C位的強烈編舞也少不了，基本上原版跟IZ*ONE版本只有些微差距。<br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn2.ettoday.net/images/3758/d3758344.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn2.ettoday.net%2Fimages%2F3758%2Fd3758344.jpg&h=aede33cf&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n▲IZ*ONE出道曲《La Vie en Rose》獲得非常好的成績。（圖／CJ E&amp;M提供）<br />\n<br />\n不過編舞版的背景音樂，在短短一分鐘的影片中，有粉絲神通廣大聽出各成員的part，有真先唱開頭，依序是丞延、Elkie、睿恩、恩彬，在上述強烈編舞的恩菲部分，原來是主唱承姬負責，最後是泰籍成員Sorn。韓網留言道：「CLC孩子們太可憐了，歌都錄好了，甚至聽說還練習了拿著玫瑰花的編舞」、「CLC錯失了大紅的機會了」為她們感到可惜。"},{"pid":"5187c82367aeb590c1d82f613946be09f8aef105","tid":1003374,"uid":181527,"like":40,"dislike":5,"score":35,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-31T15:11:02.000Z","msg":"Clc 明明之前都有幾首好歌<br />\n咪一樣唔紅 賴咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7f54b45663e5f264c92d9ba8ce875752378ade44","tid":1003374,"uid":46435,"like":62,"dislike":0,"score":62,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-01-31T15:19:22.000Z","msg":"比咩歌IZONE唱都會紅 不過CLC都叫講得幾大體 算係咁"},{"pid":"d29e957cfeff04a73c2f8942d3ddaf69da188314","tid":1003374,"uid":74065,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"7f54b45663e5f264c92d9ba8ce875752378ade44","tid":1003374,"uid":46435,"like":62,"dislike":0,"score":62,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-01-31T15:19:22.000Z","msg":"比咩歌IZONE唱都會紅 不過CLC都叫講得幾大體 算係咁"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-31T15:24:22.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3d1e167e3feeaa88197ea403eeaeea5b06e23731","tid":1003374,"uid":52073,"like":7,"dislike":9,"score":-2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-01-31T15:30:01.000Z","msg":"izone襯地淋啦!"},{"pid":"f935e0b5aa3d03fd2005f7cb30889a79d9b19e9d","tid":1003374,"uid":74065,"like":4,"dislike":8,"score":-4,"quote":{"pid":"3d1e167e3feeaa88197ea403eeaeea5b06e23731","tid":1003374,"uid":52073,"like":7,"dislike":9,"score":-2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-01-31T15:30:01.000Z","msg":"izone襯地淋啦!"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-01-31T15:30:59.000Z","msg":"我都想佢地收皮(係日本)"},{"pid":"f26b4f07511f955a3af4e1b337a4240c6d396b9f","tid":1003374,"uid":43061,"like":13,"dislike":2,"score":11,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-01-31T15:43:11.000Z","msg":"人帶歌<br />\n係某D路人先怨婦咁撚樣怨"},{"pid":"dae2faab9ab1e5a84d0a627f1b1bb513bc970bd5","tid":1003374,"uid":68678,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-01-31T15:57:28.000Z","msg":"yeeun bb 撚係主唱<br />\n專業啲啦屌你<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"231a44b216c291251fcc086810d16a175dc9c49b","tid":1003374,"uid":68678,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"dae2faab9ab1e5a84d0a627f1b1bb513bc970bd5","tid":1003374,"uid":68678,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-01-31T15:57:28.000Z","msg":"yeeun bb 撚係主唱<br />\n專業啲啦屌你<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/c