:0,"replyTime":"2019-01-31T16:06:44.000Z","msg":"好老實 clc而家既情況你比首bloombloom都有可能爆到既 如果唔係一般歌都冇可能幫到佢地 成團都冇咩觀眾緣 又冇咩綜藝同活動 我諗都係到此為止"},{"pid":"ac9b00071d6048b24df73fa149514cbbc56541cd","tid":1003374,"uid":132587,"like":13,"dislike":1,"score":12,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-31T16:07:52.000Z","msg":"唔覺得clc唱呢首stage presence會好過izone<br />\nd女正太多<br />\n睇個泰妹chorus隻手了下了下不了<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0afed0aa2491d55bc16a7f74aa6cbd28659d9fd9","tid":1003374,"uid":2781,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-01T03:16:13.000Z","msg":"其實唔解散都得嘅，轉攻東南亞國家應該搵到食"},{"pid":"01df9a837e29a631a80ffcd320b2dcaaf8ffc5a7","tid":1003374,"uid":191633,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-01T07:19:50.000Z","msg":"講真<br />\n佢地啱啱出道個陣 諗住佢地係cube假假地都有淫雅打響個頭 再慢慢轉下型 應該點都會紅少少<br />\n真係無諗過佢地會霉成咁"},{"pid":"16057ccd74c11b08ee83bfdca6dd293817bae868","tid":1003374,"uid":555,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-02-01T07:21:19.000Z","msg":"樓主又反我clc"},{"pid":"d2c66df65ad3fcef6dd6dc5c4061f66ae68884e8","tid":1003374,"uid":74065,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"16057ccd74c11b08ee83bfdca6dd293817bae868","tid":1003374,"uid":555,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-02-01T07:21:19.000Z","msg":"樓主又反我clc"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-02-01T07:30:40.000Z","msg":"邊有反 我支持港女<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"73e9d1bed33a6554726e850672af8cdf7fce3cd5","tid":1003374,"uid":555,"like":2,"dislike":4,"score":-2,"quote":{"pid":"d2c66df65ad3fcef6dd6dc5c4061f66ae68884e8","tid":1003374,"uid":74065,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"16057ccd74c11b08ee83bfdca6dd293817bae868","tid":1003374,"uid":555,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-02-01T07:21:19.000Z","msg":"樓主又反我clc"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-02-01T07:30:40.000Z","msg":"邊有反 我支持港女<img src